      <title>巴西亿万富翁考虑收购法国 Verallia</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/billionaire-brazilians-said-to-weigh-buyout-of-france-s-verallia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，在法国包装公司 Verallia SA 股价持续下跌之后，巴西亿万富翁莫雷拉·萨勒斯 (Moreira Salles) 家族正在考虑对其提出私有化报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/billionaire-brazilians-said-to-weigh-buyout-of-france-s-verallia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:36:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“交易浪潮”有望提振私募股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/wall-street-beat-01-31-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Houlihan Lokey 直接配售和二级市场主管 Matt Swain 表示，私募股权公司即将收获大笔利润。他在“彭博公开市场”上表示，许多投资者在公开市场配置过多资金，这为私募股权行业抓住“交易浪潮”提供了契机。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/wall-street-beat-01-31-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼承诺废除加拿大碳税，该税似乎已死</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大针对消费燃料征收的国家碳税可能即将进入最后几周，此前接替总理贾斯汀·特鲁多担任自由党领袖的两位主要候选人均承诺废除该税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Sippel 退出，由 Rokos 接任，Thakur 成为市场主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-names-thakur-sole-global-markets-head-as-sippel-exits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司全球市场联席主管 Jason Sippel 将离职，转投对冲基金 Rokos Capital Management，而 Pranav Thakur 将接任这家华尔街最大交易部门的唯一主管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-names-thakur-sole-global-markets-head-as-sippel-exits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>咖啡价格连续第三个月上涨，供应担忧挥之不去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/coffee-set-for-biggest-jump-in-two-months-as-supply-fears-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场关注持续的供应短缺信号，纽约阿拉比卡咖啡期货有望连续第三个月上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/coffee-set-for-biggest-jump-in-two-months-as-supply-fears-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:54:37 GMT</pubDate>
